; Coverage test for select.cc lines 79-85: recursive identifier resolution
; When a select column is a binary expression (e.g., amount + total),
; get_principal_identifiers recurses into both left and right subtrees
; to determine what type of column it is. This exercises:
;   L79-80: recursion into left subtree
;   L83-85: recursion into right subtree (binary operator)

2024/01/15 Grocery Store
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Checking

2024/01/20 Gas Station
    Expenses:Transport    $30.00
    Assets:Checking

; A binary expression using amount + total triggers recursive descent
test select 'amount + total', date from posts
     $100.00 24-Jan-15
     $-50.00 24-Jan-15
      $60.00 24-Jan-20
     $-30.00 24-Jan-20
end test
